{"tid":2282160,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李玟熱舞「選曲」挑敏感神經！　陸網逼問國籍秒回：我中國香港人","createTime":"2020-11-11T15:43:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T02:35:07.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1ef346c0431c1c653a6e315e85ac27d40a0145a2","tid":2282160,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T15:43:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5263/d5263755.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5263%2Fd5263755.jpg&h=2813f36e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲華語天后李玟。（圖／翻攝李玟臉書）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早年以多首膾炙人口的經典歌曲，紅遍大街小巷的華語天后李玟，雖然已經年近半百，但依舊保持性感又健美的好身材。最近她因為疫情關係，大幅減少螢光幕前露面的機會，但她近日在社群平台，分享了一段與二姊戴著墨鏡，搭配《我是從新加坡來的》這首歌曲熱舞，結果被大陸網友逼問國籍，她也直率坦承「「我是中國香港人」。<br />\n<br />\n李玟於本月9日分享一段和二姐動感共舞的影片。畫面中李玟與姊姊都戴著墨鏡，穿著有型，雖著音樂舞動身體，而仔細聽她們跟著翩翩起舞的背景音樂，正是《我是從新加坡來的》。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5263/d5263756.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5263%2Fd5263756.jpg&h=a69cf48d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲李玟與二姊隨著《我是從新加坡來的》這首歌起舞，引來大陸網友詢問她國籍問題。（圖／翻攝李玟臉書）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能是因為歌曲有點涉及國籍的敏感問題，立刻有大陸網友在影片留言下方質問李玟「你是中國人？還是新加坡人？」對此，李玟也毫不避諱的直率回答「我是中國香港人」，但根據大陸《搜狐》報導，這篇留言已經看不見，疑似李玟留言後又刪除。"},{"pid":"43688dcaf58d3c9d99a01a6dcbfdbc0c0325425f","tid":2282160,"uid":16659,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T15:44:41.000Z","msg":"中國人就中國人 乜中國香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e14da04b43bfdeee881f904e125836fd43e1e08","tid":2282160,"uid":211461,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"43688dcaf58d3c9d99a01a6dcbfdbc0c0325425f","tid":2282160,"uid":16659,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T15:44:41.000Z","msg":"中國人就中國人 乜中國香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T16:00:52.000Z","msg":"難聽過粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30faa3152bb5d571d54747bc996e77ed4516149","tid":2282160,"uid":3976,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T16:02:24.000Z","msg":"明明係中國新加坡人"},{"pid":"67552373f7e90f8d5e1cff5adfe5179d5bee983f","tid":2282160,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T01:44:42.000Z","msg":"brandi love"},{"pid":"08c51a775beb0e9203270e0b533d5da35377e185","tid":2282160,"uid":282930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T01:47:23.000Z","msg":"阿嬸邊位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b239e6b99aa7eacd3460ad921a63f70607e2d5","tid":2282160,"uid":182624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T01:59:13.000Z","msg":"唔想認中國人但又怕得罪老細咪叫自己做中國香港人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b1f0541bb9333fa146b3469b851104d2f55675","tid":2282160,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:35:07.000Z","msg":"佢幾時做過香港人"}]}